features: Our compression bags for travel save your storage space with no vacuum needed. Just roll up these space saving bags, functioning as powerful storage solution for travel, trips and home.

Various sizes: 12 travel combo includes 5pcs Large roll size-27.5x19.5'' (70x50 cm), 5pcs Medium roll size -23.5x15.7'' (60x40 cm) and 2pcs Small roll size-19.5x13.8'' (50x35 cm). Sized right for your closet, suitcases and boarding bags.

Secure packing travel gear: Our compression travel bags use extra thick PA+PE to secure your clothes from dirt, dust and other damages. The double layer design ensures long term storage. Our travel roll up bags can be reused multiple times.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Our travel compression bag combo is a must-have essential for travel, trip, cruise, home and more! Our travel storage bag set is the go-to solution to solve all the hassle for storage when you are travelling or moving or swapping seasonal clothing in your wardrobe. Our travel space bags create up to 80% space for your clothes, blankets, pillows & towels. Simply pack all your belongings in your closet, suitcase, briefcase, backpack with our packing bags. The travel storage bag combo includes 3 sized bags- Large, Medium, Small, catering to all your need for packing a carry-on, luggage case and backpack during travelling and camping. The compression bags can also function as laundry bags and dry bags to store dirty clothes separately or keep swim gears dry.

Product Features Dual Zipper Seal The dual zipper of our roll up travel bags makes sure that the bag is fully sealed and no air get back in. Robust Material Our travel space bags are made from premium materials (PA + PE) to ensure strength and reliability, securing your clothes from dirt, dust during travel and rainy seasons. No Pump or Vacuum Needed No vacuum cleaner or a hand pump required to suck air out. Simply roll the bag from one end to the other.
12 Travel Compression Bag Combo Includes: 5 Large roll size: 27.5x19.5’’ (70x50 cm) 5 Medium roll size: 23.5x15.7’’ (60x40 cm) 2 Small roll size: 19.5x13.8’’ (50x35 cm)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fantastic Vacuum Storage Bags: A Game-Changer for Organization!!!
reviews.reviewText: I recently had the pleasure of trying out these amazing vacuum storage bags, and I must say, I'm absolutely thrilled with the results. As someone who is always looking for ways to maximize space and keep my belongings organized, these vacuum bags have proven to be a game-changer.First and foremost, the quality of these bags is outstanding. The durable material and robust zipper ensure that my items are securely sealed and protected from dust, moisture, and insects. I feel confident storing my clothing, bedding, and other textiles knowing that they are safe and well-preserved.The vacuum functionality is where these bags truly shine. With a few simple steps, I was able to remove excess air from the bags, reducing their volume by up to 80%. This not only saved an incredible amount of space in my closets and storage areas but also helped me keep everything neatly organized. The bags are compatible with most vacuum cleaners, making the process quick and effortless.I was pleasantly surprised by the versatility of these bags. Whether I needed to store bulky winter blankets or a collection of out-of-season clothing, the variety of sizes provided in the set accommodated all of my needs. Additionally, the transparent design allowed me to easily identify the contents of each bag without having to open them, which was incredibly convenient.What truly sets these vacuum storage bags apart is their long-term effectiveness. Even after weeks or months in storage, the vacuum seal remained intact, and my items emerged just as fresh and well-preserved as the day I stored them.In conclusion, these vacuum storage bags have exceeded my expectations in every way. They have helped me reclaim valuable space, protect my belongings, and maintain a tidy home. I highly recommend them to anyone looking to optimize storage space and keep their items safe and organized. These bags are a fantastic investment, and I can't imagine managing without them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars A viable solution for bulky clothes / comforters, etc.
reviews.reviewText: Buy: Yes, but the jury is still out on longevity of the material.Why: We humans are packrats to some degree. We buy tons of things to adorn our home and accentuate our comfort. Clothes and comforters are usually good examples. These are also why these bags are so useful. These items are bulky. Space hoggers. Why have a closet cabinet full of them when you can use that storage for other items unless you have large home where space isn't a issue. But for a lot of us mere mortals, space is a commodity. We use it to store the above items with great effectiveness. Winter and summer clothes rotate through these bags. Winter comforters are stored when a thin blanket will suffice. My only concern is the integrity of the bag. If it loses air then it's useless. If tears form suddenly it's pointless. But you won't know until time tells you.Price: Fair considering you get different sizes across the board.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Extremely Handy for Saving Space!
reviews.reviewText: These vacuum storage bags are fantastic! I purchased them to help organize my closet and create more space.The bags are very thick and durable. I was able to fit coats, sweaters, bedding, and other bulky items in them and suck out all the air using the hand vacuum pump that came with the set. The hand pump works great and allows you to really compress the bags down small. They can be stacked to save a ton of room.I also like that they have the double zipper seal to really lock in the vacuum. After over a month, none of the bags had let any air back in. Things stayed tightly compacted thanks to the strong seal and reliable hand vacuum pump for sucking out excess air.These are much better quality than cheaper brands I've tried in the past. The multi-color packs make it easy to quickly see what's in each bag too.For the low price, you get a lot of very large bags that can hold multiple big items and a hand pump that removes air efficiently. If you need to maximize closet space or neatly store off-season clothing or linens, I highly recommend this vacuum bag set! Extremely happy with this purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great space saver, easy to use
reviews.reviewText: These storage bags have been a life saver. The cabinet space that I have to store blankets, sheets, pillowcases, shower curtains, ect. Is pretty decent. But before I had these, the blankets went all the way to the top, you couldn't reach the ones you wanted, and they would all fall out when you tried and it would become a jumbled mess.With these my storage space availability almost tripled, (with the exception of not being able to put my weighted blanket in one) and it's a great way to be able to organize by category.Sealing and vacuuming th air tight bags was extremely easy and self explanatory. There were no holes or problems with the bags, and I was done with the task in less than a half hour. And I had A LOT lolAll in all a good product. And I got 30 bags for a really decent price. I don't see any cons to this item.
